       </div>
                                   <p>Curro provides independent school education in English and Afrikaans to learners from 3 months to Grade 12, making use of an education model based on: Christian ethos and values Child friendliness Creative thinking Positive discipline</p>
  

        <br />
    <a href="/jobs-at/curro-holdings-ltd" class="view-all2" style="margin-top:0px">Read more about this company</a>
